<font color="#ffff80">Two ducks roasted with olives.</font>

124
00:08:35,016 --> 00:08:37,393
<font color="#ffff80">Rabbit, salad? Mmm.</font>

125
00:08:37,601 --> 00:08:40,313
<font color="#ffff80">Pouilly-Jouvet '52, plus
