<font color="#ffff80">By all means.</font>

129
00:09:07,048 --> 00:09:12,511
<font color="#ffff80">Well, it begins, as it must, with
our mutual friend's predecessor.</font>

130
00:09:12,720 --> 00:09:15,931
<font color="#ffff80">The beloved, original concierge
of The Grand Budapest.</font>

131
00:09:17,308 --> 00:09:19,393
<font color="#ffff80">It begins, of course, with...</font>

132
