<font color="#ffff80">But, truly and honestly...
Oh, dear God.</font>

157
00:10:40,099 --> 00:10:41,517
<font color="#ffff80">What have you done
to your fingernails?</font>

158
00:10:41,600 --> 00:10:43,436
<font color="#ffff80">I beg your pardon? This
diabolical varnish.</font>

159
00:10:43,561 --> 00:10:45,521
<font color="#ffff80">The color is completely wrong.
Don't you like it?</font>

160
00:10:45,604 --> 00:10:48,524
<font color="#ffff80">It's not that I don't like it.
I am physically repulsed.</font>

161
00:10:49,483 --> 00:10:51,068
<font color="#ffff80">Perhaps this will soothe you.</font>

162
