<font color="#ffff80">Please. Not now.</font>

165
00:10:55,865 --> 00:10:59,410
<font color="#ffff80">"While questing once in noble
wood of gray, medieval pine,</font>

166
00:10:59,618 --> 00:11:03,789
<font color="#ffff80">"I came upon a tomb, rain-slick'd,
rubbed-cool, ethereal,</font>

167
00:11:03,998 --> 00:11:05,749
<font color="#ffff80">"'its inscription long-vanished,</font>

168
00:11:05,958 --> 00:11:08,377
<font color="#ffff80">"yet still within its
