<font color="#ffff80">In the sacristy of Santa Maria?</font>

171
00:11:14,175 --> 00:11:15,885
<font color="#ffff80">GUSTAVE H: I'll see to
it myself immediately.</font>

172
00:11:16,594 --> 00:11:20,014
<font color="#ffff80">Remember, I'm always with you.</font>

173
00:11:20,973 --> 00:11:22,266
<font color="#ffff80">I love you.</font>

