<font color="#ffff80">for 19 consecutive seasons.</font>

177
00:11:40,826 --> 00:11:42,203
<font color="#ffff80">Um... Yes, sir.</font>

178
00:11:42,328 --> 00:11:44,163
<font color="#ffff80">She's very fond of me, you know.</font>

179
00:11:44,330 --> 00:11:45,331
<font color="#ffff80">Yes, sir.</font>

180
00:11:45,539 --> 00:11:47,458
<font color="#ffff80">But I've never seen
her like that before.</font>

