00:11:48,876 --> 00:11:51,128
<font color="#ffff80">She was shaking like
a shitting dog.</font>

183
00:11:52,546 --> 00:11:53,547
<font color="#ffff80">Truly.</font>

184
00:11:53,714 --> 00:11:56,133
<font color="#ffff80">Run to the cathedral of Santa
Maria in Brucknerplatz.</font>

